data.description: Welcome home to this Charming Ranch located in the heart of Baltimore!! Just under a 1/2 acre!! 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths, 1st  floor Laundry,  Open concept, Kitchen boasts White cabinets, Stainless steel Appliances, tiled Backsplash, Granite Countertops with large Island and Bar seating, Spacious Family room, Hardwood Floors, Four Season Room/Front Porch, Oversized Master Suite w/private entrance, attached Bath with Walk-in tiled Shower, 2 closets,  Mudroom/enclosed back porch leads to Huge deck overlooking private fenced Backyard, Mature trees, Fire pit,  Updates include; Roof, HVAC, Hot Water tank, Garage Door/Opener Kitchen, Bathrooms &  Lighting, Oversized 1 car attached Garage w/Workshop!
